I am a website developer, bot, graphic designer, and cloud engineer. I learned to make a website from 2019 I learned to use javascript in 2020, i'm also learn how to use Adobe software like Photoshop, After Effect at 2021. I'm currently learning Cloud Computing. Also I'm the CEO of DANPA STUDIO ## üèÜ Achievements - MOE (Mendallion of Excellence) in LKS Nasional 2024 Lampung (Cloud Computing) - 1st LKS Province in Bengkulu (Cloud Computing) ## üî¨ Education - INTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY BANDUNG (2025-2029) - SMKN 1 Kota Bengkulu (2022-2025) - SMPN 24 Kota Bengkulu (2019-2022) ## üõ†Ô∏è Skills - Programming (HTML, CSS, Javascript, Dart, PHP, Python) - Ckoud Computing (AWS, GCP, Azure) - Graphic design (Photoshop, Illustrator) - Movie Editing (After Effect, Premiere Pro) - DevOps (Docker, Kubernetes) ## üé• Featured Video I Make
## ‚ù§Ô∏è Others See all my projects on [Projects Page](/projects) ## ‚åõ Time Line ### 2024 - I get MOE (Mendallion of Excellence) in LKS Nasional 2024 Lampung (Cloud Computing) - 1st LKS Province in Bengkulu (Cloud Computing) - I Learn [AWS](https://aws.amazon.com/) for the first time. ### 2023 - I create ARGA Game Engine using Javascript [ARGA](https://github.com/DemuraAIdev/ARGA) ### 2022 - I learn NEXTJS (Now) - I created ZERON (Bot Discord) DISCONTINUED ### 2021 - I created I.N.T.I Projects (Bot DIscord) - My first Discord bot (I created using [Discord.JS](https://discord.js.org/)). ### 2020 - I'm learning javascript for the first time. - My first Discord server (CYBERTEAM). - I join discord. - COVID-19. ### 2019 - I create myfirst website using html and css. - I learned my first HTML. ### 2010 - Moved out to Bengkulu. ### 2007 - üë∂ Born and raised in Tangerang, Indonesia üáÆüá©.
